	(285, 1, 'Preheat the oven to 350°F. Line a 13- by 18-inch rimmed baking sheet with parchment paper.\r'),
	(285, 2, 'In a large bowl, toss the walnuts, almonds, and hazelnuts with the corn syrup until evenly coated. Spread in a single layer on the prepared baking sheet. Bake, stirring once, until the nuts are toasted and caramelized, 25 to 30 minutes. Carefully transfer'),
