	(7133, 1, 'Melt butter in heavy large skillet over medium heat. Add bell peppers and sauté until tender, about 8 minutes. Stir in mushrooms. Season to taste with salt and pepper. Sauté until mushrooms are golden brown, about 5 minutes. Mix in tarragon; cook 1 minute'),
