	(7152, 1, 'Preheat oven to 350°F. Brush rimmed baking sheet with oil. Attach candy thermometer to side of heavy medium saucepan (do not allow tip to touch bottom). Add sugar and 1/4 cup water to saucepan and stir over medium heat until sugar dissolves. Increase heat'),
	(7152, 2, '*Available at Asian markets and in the Asian foods section of some supermarkets.\r'),
	(7154, 1, 'Preheat oven to 450°F. Season pork with salt and pepper.\r'),
