	(7376, 3, 'Place the mussels in a large roasting pan and distribute dollops of the butter around the pan. Cover tightly and place in the oven for 10 minutes, or until the mussels have opened."'),
	(7376, 4, 'Divide the contents of the roasting pan among four soup or pasta bowls, discarding any mussels that have not opened. Serve immediately."'),
	(7384, 1, 'Put oven rack in middle position and preheat oven to 450°F. Line a large shallow (1-inch-deep) baking pan with foil, then oil foil."'),
