	(8006, 4, 'Available at Asian markets and many supermarkets.\r'),
	(8020, 1, 'Arrange tomato slices in 1 layer on a rack set in a shallow baking pan and sprinkle on both sides with 1 teaspoon salt and 1/2 teaspoon pepper. Let drain 30 minutes.\r'),
