	(8114, 1, 'Preheat oven to 200°. Using an electric mixer, beat egg whites, cornstarch, and cream of tartar in a large bowl until frothy. Gradually beat in 1/2 cup sugar, 1 tablespoonful at a time, until stiff peaks form. Beat in fennel seeds."'),
